Subject: [PATCH] Ooo Divisions: Aurora background + carved dice

- AuroraField: reusable WebGL Aurora canvas (de-blued, dimmed), pointer
  tracking, click-bloom, IntersectionObserver pause, reduced-motion safe.
- OooDivisions: aurora as the true section background; consistent silver
  cards with electric-violet headings; indigo objective keys unchanged.
- Products/Services rendered as two carved silver "dice" (public/assets/1die.png),
  white pills with neutral midnight-black text, headings above each die.
- Full dark-indigo card border; AODA-safe contrast throughout.

